name: Rope End
description: The end of a thick rope that's been cut. The end has been knotted, and the very end is frayed.

name: Unusual Rock
description: A small rock that stands out among all others. It's partially shaped like a flat oval, with one flat edge and another broken off with a rough edge. It has a slightly bumpy texture with a pink and black mottled texture. It can be placed on its rough edge to stand up.

name: Green Rock
description: A rock. It's very green. It has a roughly spherical shape, as well as craterous marks.

name: Crab Claw
description: A crab claw. Although when it was picked up the cartilage was malleable, it has since solidified.

name: Bone Chunk
description: A mysterious bone, possibly a joint.

name: Rubber Glove
description: A rubber glove. Not in great condition. Bumped to give better grip.

name: Plastic Handle
description: A yellow plastic broken part off of something. Hollow. Made of HDPE plastic. Has the text 'www.godeepintl.ca patent pending'.
